<p><span style="font-size:130%;">Alto,</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:130%;">The evidence you've shown me is troubling. I'm authorizing you to utilize my Level-5 certification in order to track down what he's up to, and make sure we don't have a repeat of <a href="/olympia-project">last time.</a></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:130%;">&#8212;O5-2<br /></span></p>
