<p><em><span style="color: #990011">J. Bright (Level-4 Clearance)</span></em></p>
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">.</span><br />
&#8230;<br />
<span style="font-size:0%;">.</span></p>
<p><em><span style="color: #990011">J. Bright</span></em></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="outside">
<p>Underhanded fucks, the both of 'em.</p>
<p>&quot;Goddamn it, Bright, I didn't really think you would ever actually go this far.&quot;</p>
<p>And just how</p>
<p>fucking deep</p>
<p>did you two</p>
<p>bury this shit?</p>
</div>



<div class="colmod-block">
